#   Builds against N64ModernRuntime 78949d6 (matching depth-counter ++/-- in
#   recomp_handle_tailcalls). Carries gated PSR_CFDIAG recomp_cf_note
#   scaffolding (no-op when off) — cleanup owed.
# 755b13a "fix(recompiler): handle local tailcall continuations" — call
#   wrappers consume pending tailcall targets that resolve to labels in the
#   current generated function, while pending non-local tailcalls inside an
#   existing dispatcher bubble back to that dispatcher instead of recursively
#   nesting host dispatch loops. Required for GB Tower audio verification;
#   Red/Yellow/Blue launch and play with audio on PSR dev/clear-issues.
# 5173e0f "fix(recompiler): reentrant nested tailcall dispatch — resolve
#   register-quit over-unwind" — USER-VERIFIED fix for ISSUES #7. Call
#   wrappers no longer bubble up into the outermost dispatch loop; nested
#   continuations drain their own tailcall chain locally; static-tail
#   guards (jump-to-own-return → normal return) restored. GB Tower R/B/Y
#   regression-checked OK. Builds against N64ModernRuntime main 67f3c7c
#   (reentrant recomp_handle_tailcalls). Includes gated PSR_CFDIAG
#   recomp_cf_note scaffolding (no-op when off) — cleanup owed.
